Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來身材蠻修長的 真是叫人羨慕…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.10,0:02:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去之後馬上刮你的鬍子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，唯有鬍子不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.39,0:02:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#21嗨！吻仔魚乾劫機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.94,0:02:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，居然被設計了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.44,0:02:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之，事到如今只好快點找出犯人才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.38,0:02:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是要怎麼找呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.41,0:02:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們穿這樣太引人注意了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.72,0:02:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們明明有五個人居然那麼沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅琳少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.69,0:02:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佯裝成空姐就能解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.83,0:02:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼簡單的事難道你們想不到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.90,0:02:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來少校也搭乘這艘太空船啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是巧合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.10,0:02:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為華克中校給了我一張渡假行星的旅遊機票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.24,0:02:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此，空姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.58,0:03:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.14,0:03:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是為了想假扮成空姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.32,0:03:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你襲擊她幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，原來是這樣啊\N梅琳少校也被中校．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.65,0:03:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.89,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這表示中校根本不信任你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思，請給我一杯水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.23,0:03:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.37,0:03:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好險，我們的身份差點被揭穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走開走開，沒什麼好看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，身份沒有被揭穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.97,0:03:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.28,0:03:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身高170公分，身材削瘦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.12,0:03:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?有沒有犯人的蹤跡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.96,0:03:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.12,0:03:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都坐在位子上根本看不出身高差異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.00,0:03:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就叫大家站起來不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.39,0:04:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.74,0:04:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，就是這個，梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個啦，梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.11,0:04:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好，你們都是乖孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.81,0:04:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要大吵大鬧不然她真的會開槍喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個．．．蘭花，能不能過來一下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.98,0:04:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在很忙，等一下好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以讓你等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.32,0:04:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是笨蛋吧，是笨蛋對吧沒錯，\N你們是笨蛋，笨蛋．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.19,0:04:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託，現在亂成一團\N你帶那個噁心的傢伙來幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.79,0:04:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這個人身高170公分，體重50公斤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的假的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.43,0:04:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優，你立下大功了這傢伙一定是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.87,0:04:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，怎麼看都像犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.11,0:04:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位，請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草找到的這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.71,0:04:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身高體重也跟中校的資料一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.68,0:04:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.88,0:04:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太麻煩了，把兩個人都當成犯人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.19,0:04:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡說八道什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要怎麼認定犯人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們手上的情報也只有身高體重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.56,0:05:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?蘭花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.66,0:05:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛剛想到一個超棒的好辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.53,0:05:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他們兩個上擂台比摔角怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.80,0:05:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點創意都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這算什麼好辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以用比賽輸贏來決定犯人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼沒問題?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早料到會有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.18,0:05:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個布拉曼修財團秘密開發的虛擬遊戲機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.28,0:05:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許派得上用場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，這是那個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.27,0:05:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在虛擬空間體驗戰鬥的遊戲機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.97,0:05:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我小時候在漫畫裏看過這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.73,0:05:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為就算讓兩個沒有戰鬥意願的人打鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本得不到任何答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.94,0:05:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以乾脆讓他們受極刑，逼他們自己招供比較快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.51,0:05:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這和模擬遊戲無關嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這根本是旁門左道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，那麼大家一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,悶絕悶絕，地獄攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.82,0:06:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，兩個人馬上就招了耶\N(我是犯人)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.86,0:06:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不那麼說的話鐵定會被殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.83,0:06:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦，這種畜牲傢伙說的話根本不能相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.20,0:06:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你比畜牲還要低級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事件順利解決太好了，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.90,0:06:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事件解決了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.81,0:06:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們連調查都沒做不要隨便定別人的罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.17,0:06:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從剛才一直沒有看到香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她到哪裏去了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔，她到哪裏去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.82,0:06:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草該不會被劫機犯抓去當人質了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.69,0:06:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.31,0:06:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的很莫名其妙耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.86,0:06:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才你還說他們兩個是犯人不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.83,0:06:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.27,0:06:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這是幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.80,0:06:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草是我們重要的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.94,0:06:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們要盡快把她從犯人的魔掌裏救出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劫機嫌疑犯就在這裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.48,0:07:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你懂不懂啊!地球有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?什麼危險?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.91,0:07:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位旅客請注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.36,0:07:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在本機被神秘集團劫機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.63,0:07:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我猜得果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.65,0:07:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在哪裏?她一定是在說我們啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.69,0:07:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之，分頭去找香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.53,0:07:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下，這些噁心的人怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.42,0:07:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，你在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.31,0:07:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在哪裏?香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的，快點出來啦，香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為發生了這些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.45,0:07:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.78,0:07:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，我查了一下身份背景\N這兩個人根本不是什麼犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，真是可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們有找到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.76,0:07:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.96,0:07:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到處都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.20,0:07:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草那傢伙到底跑到哪裏去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.73,0:07:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這裏幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.14,0:07:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，佛特，因為這裏沒人坐所以不小心就．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.61,0:08:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不小心你個頭啦\N你怎麼可以坐在客人座位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好不容易裝扮成空姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.11,0:08:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬一我們的身份被其他旅客拆穿怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.78,0:08:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你說，事到如今被拆穿還比較輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大姊姊，這個位子有人坐喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.32,0:08:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐在這個位子的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從飛機起飛後就不曉得到哪裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.83,0:08:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.83,0:08:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說，這個位子的人就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.17,0:08:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這位乘客提出的個人資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.81,0:08:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全查不到相關佐證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.25,0:08:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該沒錯他就是艾克塞爾·西歐雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.82,0:08:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花，這艘太空船裏還有哪裏沒找過的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.66,0:08:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只剩下船外和駕駛艙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.98,0:08:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.67,0:08:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，等著啊  我馬上來救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，你平安無事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.63,0:09:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是什麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.84,0:09:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你害人家擔心死了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.41,0:09:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草根本不需要你擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.58,0:09:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我抱抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.14,0:09:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，找到香草了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.41,0:09:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，劫機犯也順利逮捕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.32,0:09:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託，這個．．．他不是犯人，應該是機長吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.79,0:09:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,答對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.75,0:09:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草跟我只是來參觀駕駛艙而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.95,0:09:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，你們幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到那只貍貓小鬼說的話了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才是老太婆咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.43,0:09:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞什麼，原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.39,0:09:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點都不好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.54,0:09:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下我們越來越像犯人了不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.67,0:09:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得這下真的慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.27,0:09:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.47,0:09:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個叫艾克塞爾的劫機犯也不在這裏耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這都要怪你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.85,0:09:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幹嘛突然打我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.91,0:09:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謎底終於全部揭曉了艾克塞爾·西歐雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.28,0:09:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.49,0:10:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你在背後操控佛特的思考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.19,0:10:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我們天使隊為你背負劫機犯的罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是高招啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.10,0:10:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，難怪梅琳少校舉止有點怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.90,0:10:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這還不都是你們害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.94,0:10:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且艾克塞爾是個男人為什麼我這個女人．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾克塞爾是男的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前就覺得很可疑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確，這個人最近越來越男性化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.49,0:10:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們根本錯誤連篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.29,0:10:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那請你證明給我們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.53,0:10:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你讓我們看看你是佛特·修特倫的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.83,0:10:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊，就讓你們看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.37,0:10:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,證明我是佛特而且是女人的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.14,0:10:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還沒睡啊，哲郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的，媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.51,0:10:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被逼看到不想看的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.38,0:10:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣無厘頭鬧下去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.42,0:10:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然最後沒有找到艾克塞爾·西歐雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，看來可以平安抵達目的地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.59,0:11:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.32,0:11:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要結局是好的一切就0K
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.33,0:11:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天使 Rock'n'Roll
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.70,0:11:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老套的樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.97,0:11:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊搖擺搖擺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.40,0:11:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旋轉的宇宙也在跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是清白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.81,0:11:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劫機犯是艾克塞爾·西歐雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然抓不到艾克塞爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.52,0:11:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從整起事件的過程來看你們怎麼看都像犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.68,0:11:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的渡假行星我嚮往的海灘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.92,0:11:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都是你害的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，給我記住艾克塞爾·西歐雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.66,0:11:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個時候艾克塞爾·西歐雷呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(可惡!給我記住!銀河天使!)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.53,0:11:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜拳十三奧義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.33,0:11:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始羅，剪刀石頭布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.67,0:11:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黃昏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.44,0:11:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黃昏會令人感到悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.14,0:11:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該可以流淚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雨下個不停?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.51,0:12:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，都蘭行星這一年來聽說雨一直下個不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.92,0:12:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是亂來的異常氣象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且驚人的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.12,0:12:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,整個星球的平衡依然正常維持著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.46,0:12:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有雨沒完沒了的下著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.80,0:12:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個也就是說．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.23,0:12:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,八成是遺失文明造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.27,0:12:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#22藍色憂鬱雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.15,0:12:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實都蘭軍附屬的這個研究機構
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也得到了相同的結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.89,0:12:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此才麻煩遺失文明的專家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.95,0:12:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是你們天使隊來這裏幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,專家是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之首先要讓你們看個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.77,0:12:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.55,0:13:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可愛的女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個女生是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.95,0:13:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一年前戰爭的時候在保護機構遇見的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭孤兒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.56,0:13:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說要讓我們看的就是這個女孩嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.13,0:13:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，不是這個女孩你們看得見嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.87,0:13:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這孩子胸部上的寶石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道那就是遺失文明?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.81,0:13:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.11,0:13:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我立刻準備進行分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.28,0:13:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，能請你來幫忙一下嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.66,0:13:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，薄荷，請等一下我也要幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.73,0:14:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就好了請稍微忍耐一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.33,0:14:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，你要不要看雜誌或是什麼的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.50,0:14:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏又不是美容院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.74,0:14:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.51,0:14:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.88,0:14:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不曉得為什麼這女孩的體內組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.19,0:14:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與這個遺失文明緊緊地結合在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.90,0:14:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是說這個女孩一輩子無法拿掉這些寶石嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.76,0:14:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能查出這個遺失文明的成分和結構或許有辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.66,0:14:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠我們至今收集的資料也無法比對出這個遺失文明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.40,0:14:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.28,0:14:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊連你們也無能為力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.45,0:14:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在正在比對托朗斯巴皇軍過去的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.62,0:14:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重新調查有無相同案例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.76,0:14:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是現階段若查不比那個寶石的由來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.26,0:15:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就無法得知它與異常氣候有無關聯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.16,0:15:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉，幫不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，這不是你們的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.10,0:15:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這．．．這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.81,0:15:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雨這樣每天下個不停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.80,0:15:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗的衣服都乾不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很頭痛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.68,0:15:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果只是下雨還好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.82,0:15:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地域紛爭民族和宗教的對立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.59,0:15:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有因此造成的極度貧困
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.53,0:15:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這幾十年來都蘭未曾停止過戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多人死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.20,0:15:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多人離開都蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.47,0:15:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概就在這場雨開始下了一年左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.45,0:15:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為雨的影響許多糾紛戰爭也都停戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.88,0:16:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是卻有更多人離開了這個逐漸沉入水中的都蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.39,0:16:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如今留在這個星球上的只有貧困的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.93,0:16:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及一小撮的偽善者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.43,0:16:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家一定都很疲憊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.11,0:16:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要一起喝杯茶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像這樣把熱水注入茶壺裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後再把它悶一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.19,0:16:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣茶包也能泡出不輸一般茶葉泡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好喝的紅茶喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.16,0:16:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你討厭喝紅茶嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.17,0:16:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.67,0:16:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我其實很想把黏在你身上的遺失文明拿下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.28,0:17:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是現在的我只能泡紅茶給你喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.85,0:17:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏也．．．下雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.55,0:17:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是下雨啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.16,0:17:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，這個地方的確走到哪裏都在下雨喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.73,0:17:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在想到了一件很棒的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.54,0:17:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教授，事情不妙了少女失蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.31,0:17:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!說失蹤了就沒事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不快點去找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.71,0:17:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.52,0:17:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是太聰明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.38,0:17:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開著紋章機就能到沒有下雨的上空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來一場空中散步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.86,0:17:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶爾還是要離開房間到外面走一走比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.46,0:17:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然人會變得笨笨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.13,0:17:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.80,0:18:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優帶著那個女孩不曉得飛到哪裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.47,0:18:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.78,0:18:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.94,0:18:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是你們夥伴幹的好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.11,0:18:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊急聯絡空軍，立刻出動攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，怎麼突然要攻擊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.39,0:18:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要遺失文明在她身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.45,0:18:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個少女就是政府的最高機密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果你們的夥伴居然把她強行奪走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.64,0:18:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不能放著不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.96,0:18:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看樣子現在跟他說什麼都沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.90,0:18:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.90,0:18:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣?喜不喜歡空中散步呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.64,0:18:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就能到雲層上面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.61,0:18:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏也在下雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你剛才說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.22,0:18:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻回頭，乖乖的回頭進入我們的監視範圍內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.61,0:18:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你被懷疑有強行奪走遺失文明的嫌疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻掉頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.26,0:18:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼強行奪走?這樣太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.43,0:18:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只是在空中散步而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.14,0:19:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若不聽從警告的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草，有什麼不對勁嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.68,0:19:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女孩和這個星球的波長感應相互呼應著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.65,0:19:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.85,0:19:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你早就知道了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.56,0:19:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就請他們馬上停止攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.93,0:19:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去那名少女的話這場雨的原因也．．．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.76,0:19:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教授，難道你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.67,0:19:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女孩如果死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.73,0:19:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她與都蘭的意識結合會消滅雨就會停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.50,0:19:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個可能性是很高沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.81,0:19:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你該不會是認真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.51,0:19:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們真的很累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.98,0:19:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要能讓這場雨停用任何手段都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.69,0:20:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們好像逃過一劫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要緊吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.10,0:20:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?她到哪裏去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.88,0:20:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，你平安無事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在看這朵花嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.82,0:20:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可憐一定是我們迫降時掃到它的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.55,0:20:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像做了壞事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.62,0:20:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，看它這個樣子應該不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.96,0:20:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花的生命力可是很強的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.49,0:20:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算受了點傷只要讓它曬曬陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.73,0:20:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又會精神奕奕的綻放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.30,0:20:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，帶這朵花去陽光照得到的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.77,0:20:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣它一定能恢復元氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.51,0:20:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，沒問題，可以飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.28,0:20:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸運星，出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.97,0:21:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，雲層的上方永遠都是陽光普照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.18,0:21:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然預定的散步有了一點改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.91,0:21:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，為了這朵花也是沒辦法的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.28,0:21:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然曬了太陽也不會馬上恢復元氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.39,0:21:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是只要慢慢的花時間照顧它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定會開得很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.95,0:21:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像用茶包泡紅茶一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.14,0:22:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學長，我喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.67,0:22:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，這樣啊其實我也對你有好感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.88,0:22:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事怎樣都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.58,0:22:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡學長所以我要變成跟蹤狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.86,0:22:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽我說，我也喜歡你所以沒有必要變成跟蹤狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.15,0:22:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有辦法壓抑我的感情你會覺得很困擾嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.15,0:22:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟蹤狂當然很困擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.42,0:22:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要跟蹤了我們好好交往不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.12,0:22:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你果然還是不喜歡我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.36,0:22:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了，我死心了，再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.23,0:22:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.66,0:22:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啟動認真模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.60,0:22:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道該怎麼辦
